commentAnnotations.text: Subjects are not allowed to change their insulin administration methods (MDI or CSII) throughout the study.
Blinded dapagliflozin 10 mg kit contains 2 bottles of dapagliflozin 5 mg film-coated tablets (35 count)
Blinded dapagliflozin 5 mg kit contains 1 bottle of dapagliflozin 5 mg film-coated tablets and 1 bottle of placebo
If a lead-in subject fails lead-in prior to the Day 1 visit, the CGM will not be required to be completed
Tubal Ligation in this protocol is not considered surgical sterilization
